OL,3,CSecondary school attendance in Wales
OL,4,Cremains a 'national concern', report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FSecondary school attendance across
OL,8,FWales remains significantly below pre-
OL,9,Fpandemic levels, according to
OL,10,Finspection body Estyn.
OL,12,FAn updated report from Estyn, an
OL,13,Findependent Education and Training
OL,14,FInspectorate for Wales, revealed that,
OL,15,Falthough there has been improvements
OL,16,Fin secondary school attendance across
OL,17,FWales, "it still remains significantly
OL,18,Fbelow pre-pandemic levels and
OL,19,Fcontinues to be a national concern."
