OL,3,CSecondary school attendance in Wales
OL,4,Cremains a 'national concern', report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe updated report builds on findings
OL,8,Ffrom their original publication from
OL,9,FJanuary 2024.
OL,11,F"Despite early signs of improvement,
OL,12,Fprogress in tackling attendance issues
OL,13,Fis still too slow in a minority of
OL,14,Fschools," Chief Inspector for Estyn,
OL,15,FOwen Evans, said.
OL,17,FHe added that support remains
OL,18,Finconsistent across Wales, and that
OL,19,Flimited data continues to hinder
OL,20,Fschools' ability to evaluate impact
OL,21,Fand targets effectively.
