OL,3,CSecondary school attendance in Wales
OL,4,Cremains a 'national concern', report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FRecent data from the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fhighlights that attendance for
OL,9,Fsecondary schools has increased by
OL,10,F1.1%. However, this remains lower than
OL,11,Fpre-pandemic levels.
OL,13,FData from 2023-2024 shows pupils are
OL,14,Fmissing an average of nearly 11 more
OL,15,Fdays of school a year than they were
OL,16,Fbefore the pandemic.
