OL,3,CSecondary school attendance in Wales
OL,4,Cremains a 'national concern', report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FIf the current rate of improvement was
OL,8,Fto continue, Estyn says it would take
OL,9,Fover 10 years for the attendance rates
OL,10,Fto return to how they were pre-
OL,11,Fpandemic.
OL,13,FIn December 2024, the Welsh Government
OL,14,Fannounced #7million of funding to
OL,15,Fsupport school attendance and re-
OL,16,Fengagement with schools.
