OL,3,CSecondary school attendance in Wales
OL,4,Cremains a 'national concern', report
OL,5,Csays
OL,7,FThe Welsh Government said: "Raising
OL,8,Fschool attendance is a key commitment.
OL,9,FWe welcome this updated report from
OL,10,FEstyn and will be considering their
OL,11,Fnew and revised recommendations.
OL,13,F"School attendance has increased by
OL,14,F0.5% this year and we continue to
OL,15,Finvest in Family Engagement Officers
OL,16,Fand Community Focused Schools to
OL,17,Frespond to the needs of learners and
OL,18,Fbuild strong partnerships with
OL,19,Ffamilies and the wider community."
